descriptionHtml:
This is my second upload to the Nexus. She is a drow character.She is inside Helgen keep and hasnt yet followed Hadvar.

She has already picked up the Helgen keep key. There is black dragonscale armour and bloodline armour dropped around her along with crafting manuals from the draconic bloodline armour mod. It's not a necessary mod. The armour just wont be on the ground if you don't download the armour.She is wearing it in the screenshots.
